msgctxt "108_Worried Woman"
msgid "Oh, uh... Um... It's just, a friend of mine borrowed some money from a loan company that's been pressuring her to pay them back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120_Akiyama"
msgid "I see. Well, it may sound strange coming from me, but people shouldn't borrow money if they can help it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132_Worried Woman"
msgid "But if your friend's really in a jam, tell her to drop by my office. I may be able to help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144_Worried Woman"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156_Akiyama"
msgid "Tell your friend now, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168_Worried Woman"
msgid "All right... Thank you."
msgstr ""

